{"tid":855630,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉湖兩房勁劈1球易手 僅售462萬","createTime":"2018-10-10T07:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T14:58:08.000Z","uid":62935,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d976dece328eae66909acf02ccb56d116e7ff0a6","tid":855630,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:20:09.000Z","msg":"嘉湖兩房勁劈1球易手 僅售462萬<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181010&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58777928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181010%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58777928&d=ikXPlu%2B772jIrOP3wM5HetU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9ee10107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181010%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58777928&h=52f7a019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181010&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58777928</a><br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣陳嘉興表示，天水圍嘉湖山莊剛錄得一宗震撼劈價，為賞湖居6座低層E室，實用面積448方呎，昨晚施政報告前以462.3萬元成交，呎價10,319元，形容比同類兩房造價「高位回落近一球」，重返年初價。同座中高層E室，面積相同，今年6月成交價高達561萬元，呎價12,522元，其樓下單位最新造價大跌18%。<br />\n<br />\n據知，該單位今年7月放盤，開價568萬元，上月已減至538萬元，看淡後市，累減105.7萬元終沽出。單位於2015年6月以368萬元買入，賺94.3萬元離場，升幅26%。<br />\n<br />\n新買家為上車客，今年初已搵樓，預算450萬元買嘉湖山莊兩房，惟當時樓價越睇越貴，由3月搵到6月，屋苑兩房已升至550萬元，慶幸那一刻沒有盲目追價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有個業主450唔肯賣...<br />\n而家唔知450賣唔賣得出...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99fba1066bf4553c4b6b1b9982b0358a9a86d04","tid":855630,"uid":41963,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"嘉湖唔計"},{"pid":"bc761245e910edb982fc65cd6639876b63a5c184","tid":855630,"uid":33730,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"未跌夠, 大西北跌到5千蚊呎就差唔多"},{"pid":"da8dc2be0670d1337ae93a998f45acf07116cc8e","tid":855630,"uid":10290,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10