tid":855630,"uid":103921,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0f0cded954ad20b1d28383c54925f1d9357c3ca3","tid":855630,"uid":62935,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n高一層起碼十萬<br />\n<br />\n所以高層就應該賣貴兩百萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"入去睇下成交紀錄，原來又係劈完都仲係市價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁都拎出黎打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"市價？<br />\n上兩星期480-490<br />\n上兩個月5球中<br />\n<br />\n近幾個月好似未成過四球中？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"你講緊叫天價再劈20%？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/164430_920730d3246df543dfdd1818184d8eaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F164430_920730d3246df543dfdd1818184d8eaa.jpg&h=2c735ef6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ca9de298cf370201ceb7f08ba1ae1e99893e5d1","tid":855630,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"天水圍唔計"},{"pid":"cc4dd255a22929d2d9e8536b56434e55407c16a1","tid":855630,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d976dece328eae66909acf02ccb56d116e7ff0a6","tid":855630,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:20:09.000Z","msg":"嘉湖兩房勁劈1球易手 僅售462萬<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181010&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58777928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181010%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58777928&d=ikXPlu%2B772jIrOP3wM5HetU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9ee10107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181010%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58777928&h=52f7a019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181010&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58777928</a><br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣陳嘉興表示，天水圍嘉湖山莊剛錄得一宗震撼劈價，為賞湖居6座低層E室，實用面積448方呎，昨晚施政報告前以462.3萬元成交，呎價10,319元，形容比同類兩房造價「高位回落近一球」，重返年初價。同座中高層E室，面積相同，今年6月成交價高達561萬元，呎價12,522元，其樓下單位最新造價大跌18%。<br />\n<br />\n據知，該單位今年7月放盤，開價568萬元，上月已減至538萬元，看淡後市，累減105.7萬元終沽出。單位於2015年6月以368萬元買入，賺94.3萬元離場，升幅26%。<br />\n<br />\n新買家為上車客，今年初已搵樓，預算450萬元買嘉湖山莊兩房，惟當時樓價越睇越貴，由3月搵到6月，屋苑兩房已升至550萬元，慶幸那一刻沒有盲目追價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有個業主450唔肯賣...<br />\n而家唔知450賣唔賣得出...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:48:42.000Z","msg":"嘉湖堅指標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升市升包尾，跌市火車頭<br />\n<br />\n發達方程式：<br />\n以後見嘉湖大升就係時候賣樓，<br />\n嘉湖大跌完就係時候買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf2ffcd3c199f23875607d46819157875e65163","tid":855630,"uid":7206,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"平一球咪又係接火棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔明啱啱開始跌都走去買樓嘅人諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140bb75d6385bbf9d3ed7031fdff3df553a0d19b","tid":855630,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"根本重升緊"},{"pid":"b4f59ad8cdf72075a1441d107df642aa995e1559","tid":855630,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:55:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37205c58fb9084c5d13de0fa3d72c903d6ad3080","tid":855630,"uid":47776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6cf2ffcd3c199f23875607d46819157